Get Bruce Schneier's "Applied Cryptography", John Wiley & Sons,
isbn 0-471-59756-2. Also, write to author at schneier@chinet.com
and get his errata. You can also send an additional $30.00
to the author and get a floppy disk with code mentioned
in the book.

